381
00:22:43,310 --> 00:22:46,550
Entré y salí innumerables veces.

382
00:22:47,480 --> 00:22:51,440
Ya fuera viento, lluvia o granizo,

383
00:22:52,070 --> 00:22:53,440
Siempre estaba corriendo

384
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:58,110
