403
00:23:58,680 --> 00:23:59,480
I...

404
00:24:00,340 --> 00:24:02,940
Extraño a Jintai.

405
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:12,830
Vamos.

406
00:24:14,350 --> 00:24:16,790
Con ustedes dos protegiéndome,

407
00:24:17,310 --> 00:24:20,030
